		p Openland reserves the right to change this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes to this Privacy Policy will become effective on the "Effective Date" indicated above. If you continue to use the service after those changes took effect, you consent to the new Policy. Openland will always have the latest Policy posted on the Service.

